  "texts": [
    "offers their services to EU citizens.",
    "This therefore brings global technologies such as LLMs and other AI models such as Chat-GPT, Bard, Gemini, etc., squarely under the GDPR where these are accessible from the European Union.",
    "All processing of personal data within the scope of the GDPR requires a legal basis, article 6(1) GDPR.",
    "The question of the legal basis for data processing across the life cycle of a generative AI system poses different problems, as it depends on the stage of the data processing.",
    "As argued before, it is essential to distinguish between the different steps of data processing when analysing AI and data protection (Mühlhoff & Ruschemeier, 2024a)."
  ]
}